OL,5,G0600 Teleshopping
OL,6,G0700 Shop: Thane Offers
OL,7,     FVisit Thane.tv and browse our
OL,8,     Fselection of award winning home
OL,9,     Fand fitness products that let you
OL,10,     Fdo more with less!
OL,11,G0730 JML Presents
OL,12,     FShop JML, the home for clever
OL,13,     Fideas.
OL,14,G0800 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,15,     FHairdresser and salon owner
OL,16,     FDennis, from Dundee, has a busy
OL,17,     Fday of bookings. But there is an
OL,18,     Fissue with a leaky water pipe,
OL,19,     Fwhich, if it can't be fixed, may
OL,20,     Fmean shutting the salon.
