OL,5,G1700 Call the Bailiffs: Time to Pay Up
OL,6,     FFollowing the work of agents
OL,7,     Fexecuting writs on behalf of
OL,8,     Fpeople desperate to recover money
OL,9,     Fowed. In Coventry, agents call in
OL,10,     Fthe police when a tenant becomes
OL,11,     Fthreatening.
OL,12,G1800 Home and Away
OL,13,     FSonny refuses to play by the
OL,14,     Frules. Cash's turnaround is
OL,15,     Fshort-lived. Justin catches a
OL,16,     Flucky break.
OL,17,G1830 New: Home and Away
OL,18,     FAbigail works to persuade
OL,19,     FMackenzie. Richie's day goes from
OL,20,     Fbad to worse. Alf's unable to
OL,21,     Fenjoy the win.
