OL,5,G1900 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FThe doctors and nurses at the
OL,7,     Fpractice take measures to minimise
OL,8,     Fthe over-prescription and overuse
OL,9,     Fof antibiotics in the face of a
OL,10,     Flooming crisis.
OL,11,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,12,     FTwo critically ill children are
OL,13,     Frushed in by ambulance within ten
OL,14,     Fminutes of each other.
OL,15,     FTen-year-old Kai has been having
OL,16,     Fseizures, and 18-month-old Joel is
OL,17,     Fstruggling to breathe.
