OL,5,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,6,     FFour top dermatologists treat
OL,7,     Fpatients for skin conditions such
OL,8,     Fas cysts, lipomas and skin tags
OL,9,     Fthat the NHS views as cosmetic but
OL,10,     Fthat can affect sufferers.
OL,11,G0000 Scam City
OL,12,     FHost Conor Woodman is in Rome, on
OL,13,     Fa mission to uncover the gritty
OL,14,     Funderworld that crawls under its
OL,15,     Fthriving tourist scene.
OL,16,G0100 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,17,     FAt the Hall Green Health Centre,
OL,18,     FDr Ashraf speaks to a man who has
OL,19,     Freturned from a holiday in Egypt
OL,20,     Fand may have picked up something
OL,21,     Fwith serious repercussions.
